        "Fast Track Process is available for renewable projects under 5 MW at MISO and SPP\n[...]\nThere is a fast track process for project sizes less than 5 MW with the entire process takes less than 90 days. Yes, the criteria to qualify for fast track is detailed, but if the project qualifies – renewable developers would be better served to take this step towards connecting to the wholesale markets."
      ]
    }
  ]
